<br>
I think ive GAINED from using a macro, if we are mid fight and i see a mob that needs CC, i can tell someone to pick it up in channel without worrying about a song droping. Makes giving instructions mid fight alot easier.<br>
<br>
Sure an auto twist feature or extended song durations might dumb up the class some and (god forbid) allow more people to play them. But a good bard is still gonna be a good bard jus like a good cleric is still a good cleric and a good paladin is still a good paladin. Idiots will still be idiots no matter how easy you make the class to play. Lets not think that jus because we have mashed keys every 3 seconds in a certain order for the last 4 years we are some how better or more skillful than everyone else.<br>
<br>
I think the pros outweigh the cons when it comes to having extended song durations or a 3 song auto-twist ability.<br>
